text.tspan: Both electric and telephone "aj" connectors attached to the cold water pipe shall
be within 5 ft (1.5 m) of where the pipe enters the premises.
Refer to Section 1755.508, Paragraph (v), Table 5 for the ground wire conductor
size. Ground wire must be accepted by a Nationally recognized testing laboratory.
Connector "aj" must be accepted by a Nationally recognized testing laboratory.
ALTERNATIVE TECHNIQUE FOR BONDING TO ELECTRIC SERVICE GROUND
WHERE DIRECT ATTACHMENT IS NOT POSSIBLE
